# Next Session: Workbench Base Components + Content Forge UI Design

**Context:** Load `pagespec/cms/ObjectTree.md` for architecture reference.
The homepage renders at `/` with data-driven components. The two-tree stitching
works. MCP tools need debugging (rpcdispatch module SQL rewire may not have
